            "description": "Return the full device list with current state.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"devices\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"10.10.1.30-0\",\n      \"device_type\": \"relay\",\n      \"name\": \"Keuken LED\",\n      \"room\": \"Keuken\",\n      \"semantic_type\": \"light\",\n      \"active\": true,\n      \"max_watt\": 60,\n      \"state\": \"off\",\n      \"current_watt\": 0,\n      \"firmware\": \"5.1\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"10.10.1.40-0\",\n      \"device_type\": \"dimmer\",\n      \"name\": \"Woonkamer Dimmer 1\",\n      \"room\": \"Woonkamer\",\n      \"semantic_type\": \"light\",\n      \"active\": true,\n      \"max_watt\": 200,\n      \"state\": \"on\",\n      \"level\": 75,\n      \"current_watt\": 150,\n      \"firmware\": \"5.4\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
